  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.8.6">
<l>vāṉavartan tuyartīra vantu tōṉṟi māṇuruvāy mūvaṭimā valiyai vēṇṭi</l>
<l>tāṉamara vēḻulaku maḷanta veṉṟit taṉimutalcak karappaṭaiyeṉ talaivaṉ kāṇmiṉ</l>
<l>tēṉamarum poḻiltaḻuvu meḻilkoḷ vītic ceḻumāṭa māḷikaikaḷ kūṭan tōṟum</l>
<l>āṉatolcīr maṟaiyāḷar payiluñ celvat taṇiyaḻuntūr niṉṟukanta vamarar kōvē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My leader with the discus weapon, superior and singular in victory, who,</l>
<l rend="indent">appearing in dwarf form,</l>
<l>Coming to end the suffering of the celestials, having begged Māvali</l>
<l rend="indent">for three feet, measured the seven worlds so he was content,</l>
<l>Behold, is the king of immortals who is happy</l>
<l rend="indent">standing in lovely, prosperous Aḻuntūr,</l>
<l rend="indent">where Vedic experts of worthy, ancient fame practice</l>
<l>As suited to every hall, pavilion, and splendid mansion</l>
<l rend="indent">along the colorful streets which nectar-filled groves embrace.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
